creator: Susanna Moodie
description:
LibriVox recording of Oh! Can You Leave Your Native Land? by Susanna Moodie.

Read in English by Bruce Kachuk; Chris Pyle; Greg Giordano; Ian King; Julia Niedermaier; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn; Rachel; and William Gair.

Librivox volunteers bring you ten recordings of Oh! Can You Leave Your Native Land? by Susanna Moodie. This was the weekly poem for the week of November 16, 2014. Summary by Rachel.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
